    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu (Doton)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 5</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 6</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 18 | <b>Successes:</b> 2</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 6 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 18</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> H</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>This technique can only be used if the target area contains a hard or rocky surface and is not underwater.<br><br>You touch the ground or a surface directly connected to it and send a shock wave through the ground, causing the target area to erupt in a spray of earth and rock, dealing 5d6 earth damage.</p>\n\n\n\n",
